snippet.title: Crazy Crime Chick
snippet.description:
Hi everyone 👋 
A little about myself I enjoy scary stories and watching scary movies late at night , my poison of choice is whiskey and I can never say no to pizza . I been following the Chris Watts Case almost from the beginning once I watched all interviews read the Discovery look at the evidence given I was left with more questions then answers I decided to create my YouTube channel because I needed an outlet and distraction from all the madness with covid-19 going on plus my boyfriend is sick of hearing about it lol . I promise to bring facts mixed with my own opinions  What I want for my  channel is to build a community where it feels like family and friends getting together talking & researching cases they just can't stop talking about I don't have a set uploading schedule yet so  Make sure you subscribe and hit that notification bell Let's get to chatting 


email
callmecrazzy48@aol.com
